  <div class="max-w-2xl my-40 mx-auto px-4 text-[16px] antialiased text-neutral-500">
    <span class="text-neutral-800 font-bold">Diego and his small team at <a href="https://familyoffice.is"><b>Family Office</b></a> articulate company-changing strategies and design resulting brand identities, user interfaces, spaces, packaging, and more.</span> The firm's previous clients have described the work as “stronger and more business-savvy than any brand strategy work we have seen before.”
    <div class="flex flex-row my-7 gap-6">
      <div class="basis-1/2 md:basis-1/2">
        <p class="block md:hidden">
        Operating from:<br />120 Walker Street <br />New York, NY 10013 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="basis-1/2 md:basis-1/2">
        <p class="hidden md:block mb-4">
        Operating from:<br />120 Walker Street <br />New York, NY 10013 
        </p>
        <p class="">
        Reachable at: <br /><a href="mailto:diego@familyoffice.is">diego@familyoffice.is</a>
        </p>
