    </div>
    <span class="text-neutral-800 font-bold">He co-founded <a href="https://terms-eccles.com"><b>Terms-Eccles</b></a> to host conversations at the intersections of finance and culture.</span> Most recently, on the evening of Tax Day, Monday April 15, 2024, legendary financial writer James Grant, bestselling author Carrie Sun, infamous it-girl Cat Marnell, and the podcast duo behind The Ion Pack came together at Spring Place for a crowd of 130. 
